    "title": "Front Office Manager - Sarovar Hotels Capital India - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "Grow your career with Sarovar Hotels Capital India! We are hiring a Front Office Manager for our Gwalior team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Sarovar Hotels Capital India:\nSarovar Hotels Capital India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sarovar Hotels Capital India!",
